title: Is The Lakers Season Over?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss the Lakers embarrassing loss to Clippers, KD’s return to Nets lineup, Luka drops a hot & spicy 41-piece on the struggling Warriors, Amari Cooper’s future in Dallas, is it time to put respect on the Celtics name, UFC 272 preview, advice for Tristan Thompson’s broke shot, plus the guys show love to Coach K. All that and more!!!
